msgstr "`vllm_ascend.attention.backends.flash_attn.FlashAttentionBackend`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:93
msgid "`vllm_ascend.attention.backends.block_attn.BlockAttentionBackend`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend.attention.backends.block_attn.BlockAttentionBackend`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:94
msgid "`vllm_ascend.attention.backends.paged_attn.PagedAttentionBackend`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend.attention.backends.paged_attn.PagedAttentionBackend`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:96
msgid ""
"Each backend stores its own capture-time state and provides the "
"corresponding update logic. The wrapper calls the generic "
"`update_full_graph_params()` entry point, which dispatches to the "
"appropriate backend."
msgstr ""
"每个后端存储其自身的捕获时状态，并提供相应的更新逻辑。封装器调用通用的 `update_full_graph_params()` 入口点，该入口点会分发到相应的后端。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:98
msgid "Piecewise graph capture and replay"
msgstr "分段图捕获与重放"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:100
msgid ""
"Piecewise mode captures one ACL graph per model layer. The wrapper "
"handles this by iterating over layers during capture and replay, "
"maintaining a list of graph entries indexed by layer index. Each entry "
"stores the captured graph, the input and output tensors, and the "
"attention-specific metadata needed for parameter updates."
msgstr ""
"分段模式为每个模型层捕获一个 ACL 计算图。封装器通过在捕获和重放期间遍历各层来处理此问题，维护一个按层索引索引的计算图条目列表。每个条目存储捕获的计算图、输入和输出张量，以及参数更新所需的注意力特定元数据。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:102
msgid ""
"During replay, the wrapper iterates through the layer graphs, updating "
"attention parameters and replaying each graph in sequence. The stream "
"synchronization and event management are handled per-layer, similar to "
"the full graph case but applied independently for each captured segment."
msgstr ""
"在重放期间，封装器遍历各层计算图，更新注意力参数并按顺序重放每个计算图。流同步和事件管理按层处理，与完整图情况类似，但独立应用于每个捕获的段。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:104
msgid "Graph pool management"
msgstr "计算图池管理"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:106
msgid ""
"ACL graph capture requires a graph pool, which is created and managed by "
"the wrapper. The pool is initialized once during the first capture and "
"reused for subsequent captures and replays. The wrapper ensures that the "
"pool is properly sized for the expected number of graphs and that it is "
"cleaned up when the model is destroyed."
msgstr ""
"ACL 计算图捕获需要一个计算图池，该池由封装器创建和管理。池在首次捕获期间初始化一次，并在后续捕获和重放中重用。封装器确保池的大小适合预期的计算图数量，并在模型销毁时正确清理。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:108
msgid ""
"The pool size is determined by the stream budget trimming logic in "
"`update_aclgraph_sizes()`. The wrapper allocates the pool with the "
"maximum expected number of graphs, and individual graph entries are "
"created and destroyed as needed during capture and replay."
msgstr ""
"池大小由 `update_aclgraph_sizes()` 中的流预算裁剪逻辑确定。封装器使用预期的最大计算图数量分配池，并在捕获和重放期间根据需要创建和销毁单个计算图条目。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:110
msgid "Error handling and fallback"
msgstr "错误处理与回退"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:112
msgid ""
"If ACL graph capture fails for any reason (e.g., resource exhaustion, "
"unsupported operator, device error), the wrapper falls back to eager "
"execution for the affected batch descriptor. The error is logged, and the "
"graph entry is marked as unavailable. Subsequent requests with the same "
"batch descriptor will continue to use eager execution."
msgstr ""
"如果 ACL 计算图捕获因任何原因失败（例如，资源耗尽、不支持的算子、设备错误），封装器会为受影响的批次描述符回退到立即执行模式。错误会被记录，计算图条目被标记为不可用。后续具有相同批次描述符的请求将继续使用立即执行模式。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:114
msgid ""
"The wrapper also handles the case where a captured graph becomes invalid "
"during replay (e.g., due to device reset or memory corruption). In this "
"case, the graph entry is invalidated and the request falls back to eager "
"execution."
msgstr ""
"封装器还处理重放期间捕获的计算图变得无效的情况（例如，由于设备重置或内存损坏）。在这种情况下，计算图条目被无效化，请求回退到立即执行模式。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:116
msgid "Performance considerations"
msgstr "性能考虑"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:118
msgid ""
"The primary performance benefit of ACL graph execution comes from "
"reducing host launch overhead. For small and medium batch sizes, this "
"overhead can be a significant fraction of total latency. The graph mode "
"amortizes this overhead by capturing the execution plan once and replaying"
" it multiple times."
msgstr ""
"ACL 计算图执行的主要性能优势来自于减少主机启动开销。对于中小批次大小，此开销可能占总延迟的很大一部分。计算图模式通过一次性捕获执行计划并多次重放来分摊此开销。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:120
msgid ""
"The overhead of graph capture itself is non-trivial and is incurred once "
"per batch descriptor. The wrapper minimizes this by caching graph entries "
"and reusing them across requests with the same batch descriptor. The "
"capture overhead is further reduced by the stream budget trimming, which "
"limits the number of graphs that need to be captured."
msgstr ""
"计算图捕获本身的开销不可忽视，每个批次描述符只产生一次。封装器通过缓存计算图条目并在具有相同批次描述符的请求之间重用它们来最小化此开销。流预算裁剪进一步减少了捕获开销，限制了需要捕获的计算图数量。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:122
msgid ""
"The attention parameter update overhead is also a consideration. The "
"host-side update stream runs concurrently with the replay stream, so the "
"update overhead is partially hidden by the execution pipeline. However, "
"for very small batch sizes, the update overhead may dominate, and the "
"benefit of graph mode may be reduced."
msgstr ""
"注意力参数更新开销也是一个考虑因素。主机端更新流与重放流并发运行，因此更新开销部分被执行流水线隐藏。然而，对于非常小的批次大小，更新开销可能占主导地位，计算图模式的收益可能会降低。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:124
msgid "Future work"
msgstr "未来工作"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:126
msgid ""
"The current implementation has several areas for improvement that are "
"planned for future releases:"
msgstr "当前实现有几个计划在未来版本中改进的领域："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:128
msgid ""
"Support for `FULL_AND_PIECEWISE` mode: Currently normalized to "
"`PIECEWISE`, but full support would allow the runtime to choose the best "
"mode per request."
msgstr ""
"支持 `FULL_AND_PIECEWISE` 模式：当前被规范化为 `PIECEWISE`，但完整支持将允许运行时为每个请求选择最佳模式。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:129
msgid ""
"Dynamic stream budget allocation: Instead of a fixed budget, the wrapper "
"could dynamically adjust the number of graphs based on available "
"resources."
msgstr ""
"动态流预算分配：封装器可以根据可用资源动态调整计算图数量，而不是使用固定预算。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:130
msgid ""
"Improved attention parameter update: Reduce the overhead of host-side "
"updates by batching or pipelining updates across layers."
msgstr ""
"改进的注意力参数更新：通过跨层批处理或流水线更新来减少主机端更新的开销。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:131
msgid ""
"Support for encoder-decoder models in full graph mode: Currently forced "
"to piecewise mode."
msgstr ""
"在完整图模式下支持编码器-解码器模型：当前强制使用分段模式。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:132
msgid ""
"Integration with Xlite graph mode: Better coordination between ACL graph "
"and Xlite graph execution paths."
msgstr ""
"与 Xlite 计算图模式的集成：更好地协调 ACL 计算图和 Xlite 计算图执行路径。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:90
msgid "This mechanism is implemented in attention backends such as:"
msgstr "此机制在注意力后端中实现，例如："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:92
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/attention_v1.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/attention_v1.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:93
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/mla_v1.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/mla_v1.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:94
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/attention_cp.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/attention_cp.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:95
msgid "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/mla_cp.py`"
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/mla_cp.py`"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:97
msgid ""
"The important design point is that Ascend full graph support depends on "
"backend-provided `update_graph_params()` hooks. Without that hook, "
"capture alone is not enough to replay the correct attention state."
msgstr ""
"重要的设计点是，Ascend 完整图支持依赖于后端提供的 `update_graph_params()` "
"钩子。没有这个钩子，仅靠捕获不足以重放正确的注意力状态。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:99
msgid "Replay ordering and synchronization"
msgstr "重放顺序与同步"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:101
msgid ""
"`ACLGraphWrapper` synchronizes the current stream before replay in the "
"common path to ensure that host-side parameter updates stay aligned with "
"the graph execution that will consume them. This is especially relevant "
"in asynchronous scheduling or multi-threaded execution."
msgstr ""
"`ACLGraphWrapper` "
"在通用路径的重放前同步当前流，以确保主机侧参数更新与将要使用它们的图执行保持对齐。这在异步调度或多线程执行中尤为重要。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:103
msgid ""
"If ordering is not preserved, the parameter update for iteration *i* can "
"be observed by the replay of iteration *i-1*, or the replay of iteration "
"*i* can start before its own parameter update has completed. In practice,"
" this means the attention operator may run with mismatched runtime "
"metadata, which can cause incorrect results, precision issues, or even "
"hangs. The code keeps a narrower path for the main full-graph eagle case,"
" but the general design assumption is the same: replay must not overtake "
"pending parameter update work."
msgstr ""
"如果顺序未得到保持，迭代 *i* 的参数更新可能被迭代 *i-1* 的重放观察到，或者迭代 *i* "
"的重放可能在它自身的参数更新完成之前就开始。实际上，这意味着注意力算子可能在运行时元数据不匹配的情况下运行，这可能导致错误结果、精度问题甚至挂起。代码为主流的完整图"
" eagle 情况保留了一条更窄的路径，但通用的设计假设是相同的：重放不得超越待处理的参数更新工作。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:105
msgid "Full vs Piecewise on Ascend"
msgstr "Ascend 上的完整图与分段图"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:107
msgid ""
"Upstream docs already define full graph and piecewise graph semantically."
" On Ascend, the practical difference is driven by backend support and "
"resource cost."
msgstr "上游文档已经在语义上定义了完整图和分段图。在 Ascend 上，实际差异由后端支持和资源成本驱动。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:109
msgid "Piecewise mode"
msgstr "分段模式"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:111
msgid ""
"Piecewise mode is the conservative path. It relies on the generic vLLM "
"split execution strategy, then applies ACL graph capture to the non-"
"attention segments selected by the compilation path. On Ascend, this mode"
" is currently the more widely supported option, but it is also the most "
"sensitive to stream pressure because the number of captured graphs scales"
" with model depth."
msgstr ""
"分段模式是保守路径。它依赖通用的 vLLM 拆分执行策略，然后将 ACL 图捕获应用于编译路径选择的非注意力片段。在 Ascend "
"上，此模式是目前更广泛支持的选项，但它也对流压力最敏感，因为捕获的图数量随模型深度而增加。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:113
msgid "Full graph mode"
msgstr "完整图模式"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:115
msgid ""
"Full graph mode is the more performance-oriented path when the attention "
"backend can support runtime parameter patching through "
"`update_graph_params()`. On Ascend, full graph support is tied to those "
"attention-specific update hooks, workspace caching, and replay ordering "
"guarantees."
msgstr ""
"完整图模式是更注重性能的路径，前提是注意力后端能够通过 `update_graph_params()` 支持运行时参数修补。在 Ascend "
"上，完整图支持与那些注意力特定的更新钩子、工作空间缓存和重放顺序保证紧密相关。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:117
msgid "Diagnostics and Operational Notes"
msgstr "诊断与操作说明"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:119
msgid ""
"The simplest way to confirm that graph mode is active is to enable "
"cudagraph metrics and keep log stats enabled. In CLI usage, use "
"`--cudagraph-metrics` and do not pass `--disable-log-stats`. In Python "
"usage, set `cudagraph_metrics=True` and `disable_log_stats=False`. Then "
"inspect the emitted metrics and logs."
msgstr ""
"确认图模式是否激活的最简单方法是启用 cudagraph 指标并保持日志统计开启。在 CLI 使用中，使用 `--cudagraph-"
"metrics` 且不传递 `--disable-log-stats`。在 Python 使用中，设置 "
"`cudagraph_metrics=True` 和 `disable_log_stats=False`。然后检查输出的指标和日志。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:120
msgid ""
"Profiling can also confirm whether replay is happening, and developers "
"can add temporary prints before replay when debugging locally, but those "
"are secondary methods and are not expanded here."
msgstr "性能分析也可以确认重放是否发生，开发者可以在本地调试时在重放前添加临时打印，但这些都是次要方法，此处不展开说明。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:121
msgid ""
"`update_aclgraph_sizes()` is the main implementation point for stream-"
"budget-driven capture-size trimming."
msgstr "`update_aclgraph_sizes()` 是基于流预算驱动的捕获大小调整的主要实现点。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:122
msgid ""
"In debug mode, `ACLGraphWrapper` asserts that replay uses the same tensor"
" addresses recorded during capture."
msgstr "在调试模式下，`ACLGraphWrapper` 断言重放使用与捕获期间记录的相同的张量地址。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:123
msgid ""
"`ASCEND_LAUNCH_BLOCKING=1` is incompatible with ACL graph enablement in "
"the current implementation."
msgstr "在当前实现中，`ASCEND_LAUNCH_BLOCKING=1` 与 ACL 图启用不兼容。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:124
msgid ""
"For debugging inside graph execution, the repo also provides graph-aware "
"print helpers in `vllm_ascend.utils`, but those are developer diagnostics"
" rather than part of the execution design."
msgstr ""
"对于图执行内部的调试，代码库还在 `vllm_ascend.utils` "
"中提供了图感知的打印辅助工具，但这些是开发者诊断工具，而非执行设计的一部分。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:126
msgid "Related Files"
msgstr "相关文件"

