msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/attention_cp.py`，上下文并行注意力更新路径。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:134
msgid ""
"`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/mla_cp.py`, context parallel MLA "
"update path."
msgstr "`vllm_ascend/attention/context_parallel/mla_cp.py`，上下文并行 MLA 更新路径。"

